    "body": "If I can add a wish list item here, I'd love v4/v6 dual-stack for P2P. Lighthouse for example does `--listen-address '0.0.0.0' --listen-address '::'` (or any combination thereof) and then P2P listens on both v4 and v6. The `0.0.0.0` is the default and then they're v4-only.\r\n\r\nErigon and Geth just do dual-stack by default, no additional parameters required. Same for Teku.",
